**Cubit**:
```dart
class UserArticlesCubit extends Cubit<UserArticlesState> {
  final GetUserArticlesUseCase getUserArticles;

  UserArticlesCubit(this.getUserArticles) : super(UserArticlesInitial());

  Future<void> fetchUserArticles() async {
    emit(UserArticlesLoading());
    final result = await getUserArticles(NoParams());
    result.fold(
      (failure) => emit(UserArticlesError(failure.message)),
      (articles) => emit(UserArticlesLoaded(articles)),
    );
  }
}
```

Use `image_picker: ^1.1.2` for gallery/camera. **Key features**:
- Form fields: TextFormField (title/author/desc), TextFormField(multi-line: content), DatePicker (publishedAt)
- Image picker button → preview Container with NetworkImage/FileImage
- Client validation: title/content/author/publishedAt required
- BlocConsumer<ArticleUploadCubit> for loading/success/error states
- Success: Navigator.pop(context, true)
- Error: SnackBar

**Pseudo-code**:
```dart
